https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8pzIuLFuv6U


in app folder, create folder called 'components' 
in components folder, create file called 'navbar.tsx'



navbar.tsx:

import Link from 'next/link'

export default function Navbar() {
  return (
    <div>
        <Link href='/'>Home</Link>
        <Link href='/aboutus'>About Us</Link>
        <Link href='/contactus'>Contact Us</Link>
    </div>
  )
}







Go into layout.tsx and add in <Navbar /> in return statement
this way the navbar will display no matter the page

  <html lang="en">
      <body className={inter.className}>
        <Navbar />
        {children}</body>
    </html>
    
    





Do same process for Footer